name: Void Gate
description:
''Void Gate'' represents the fractalization of thoughts and emotions creating the beautiful dark path of self-realization. It symbolizes the unintentional pursuit of the undesired truth, purely driven by the curiosity of the self-critical mind. 

Void Gate was exhibited as a part of the Neo Shibuya TV museum in Tokyo in November 2020.
